00:41:41,587 --> 00:41:42,386
Xiang Liu,

500
00:41:43,666 --> 00:41:44,987
after such a long time fighting,

501
00:41:45,426 --> 00:41:47,146
we finally met face to face today.

502
00:41:47,747 --> 00:41:49,107
