503
00:42:07,067 --> 00:42:07,987
It really is you.

504
00:42:09,386 --> 00:42:11,226
You're very clever.

505
00:42:11,507 --> 00:42:12,386
I'm impressed.

506
00:42:12,747 --> 00:42:13,906
In terms of intelligence,

507
00:42:14,987 --> 00:42:16,466
I'm no match for you.

508
00:42:16,987 --> 00:42:18,107
If the conditions

509
00:42:18,307 --> 00:42:19,267
were balanced today,

510
00:42:19,587 --> 00:42:20,587
I would be no match for you.

511
00:42:22,386 --> 00:42:24,706
Now, we have surrounded you
from all directions.

512
00:42:24,706 --> 00:42:25,987
There's no way out.

513
00:42:26,587 --> 00:42:27,987
Why not let go of the past

514
00:42:27,987 --> 00:42:28,987
and have a good talk with us?

515
00:42:30,186 --> 00:42:31,426
As long as you are willing,

516
00:42:32,347 --> 00:42:34,267
I can promise on behalf of His Majesty

517
00:42:36,987 --> 00:42:37,946
that you will be a king

518
00:42:38,186 --> 00:42:39,666
and granted a territory.

519
00:42:44,226 --> 00:42:46,827
If back then, Haoling was defeated

520
00:42:47,226 --> 00:42:48,507
by Xiyan,

521
00:42:50,027 --> 00:42:51,787
and Cang Xuan offered generous terms

522
00:42:52,186 --> 00:42:53,547
to let you surrender,

523
00:42:55,747 --> 00:42:56,866
would you do it?

524
00:43:14,587 --> 00:43:17,146
Even you cannot do it.

525
00:43:19,987 --> 00:43:21,146
