533
00:44:11,217 --> 00:44:15,499
♪I was unruffled
with no sorrow and soreness♪

534
00:44:17,579 --> 00:44:22,379
♪In my chaotic life,
I failed to meet your gaze♪

535
00:44:25,515 --> 00:44:27,787
♪Only emptiness remained♪

536
00:44:30,731 --> 00:44:33,803
♪Enduring all things in my life♪

537
00:44:35,652 --> 00:44:40,043
♪I valued all but indifferent
to wealth and fame♪

538
00:44:41,579 --> 00:44:47,052
♪Basking in the sun,
I couldn't feel your sunlight♪

539
00:44:48,003 --> 00:44:53,835
♪All I feel is a painful heat wave♪

540
00:44:56,683 --> 00:45:01,419
♪All things are dim,
while only your eyes shine bright♪

541
00:45:02,731 --> 00:45:07,243
♪I'll follow my heart
and go to chase the sun far away♪

542
00:45:08,683 --> 00:45:14,635
♪Everything seems sad,
while only your brows raise in delight♪

543
00:45:15,412 --> 00:45:19,723
♪I'm waiting for you
to enjoy the scenery at night♪

544
00:45:20,715 --> 00:45:25,681
♪You came with wind and rain,
